            <title>[LU-13904] Support non-modular builds</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13904</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For the upstreaming-to-linux work we will want lustre to build non-modular.&#160; Even when modular it does not need to have so many small modules.&lt;/p&gt;

